{"tid":2246223,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警繁忙時間主要幹道訓練遇車禍 議員斥擾民","createTime":"2020-10-17T01:09:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T05:59:53.000Z","uid":6497,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"930246ba7283f38eb970fdd0c7ae6ebb2c675b38","tid":2246223,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T01:09:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20201016/s00001/1602815187365/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20201016%2Fs00001%2F1602815187365%2F&d=6FpmejEDNbHOA1ae24hao%2FcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=b8f1dc48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20201016%2Fs00001%2F1602815187365%2F&h=dd97d4fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20201016/s00001/1602815187365/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20201016/s00001/d855986fcf10af9f755d72266645929a.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20201016%2Fs00001%2Fd855986fcf10af9f755d72266645929a.jpg&d=6FpmejEDNbHOA1ae24hao%2FcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=f6e7b5a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20201016%2Fs00001%2Fd855986fcf10af9f755d72266645929a.jpg&h=ff07e464\" target=\"_blank\">https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20201016/s00001/d855986fcf10af9f755d72266645929a.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n清晨6時51分，兩輛警方「大馬」電單車沿青葵公路往荃灣方向行駛，駛近荃灣路交界支路時兩車突然相撞，其中一名警員人仰馬翻倒地受傷，事後送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n涉事警員同為警隊護送組成員，當時正駕駛「大馬」進行訓練，兩車駛至上址時，其中一輛「大馬」疑收掣不及撞到前方同僚引致意外，事後警隊護送組其他隊員繼續於現場進行訓練。<br />\n<br />\n葵青區議員王天仁表示，3號幹線一向為非法賽車黑點，警方不時於該路段巡邏，但鮮有聽聞有警隊護送組演練。他指出，3號幹線為本港其中一條主要幹道，警方於早上上班繁忙時間到該路段訓練，不論規模大小均有佔用路段，今早（16日）更發生意外，難免擾民，認為警方選擇的時段不理想。"},{"pid":"474f6a997a1aef57000db1faade1e15546728f83","tid":2246223,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T01:09:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20201016/s00001/d855986fcf10af9f755d72266645929a.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20201016%2Fs00001%2Fd855986fcf10af9f755d72266645929a.jpg&d=6FpmejEDNbHOA1ae24hao%2FcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=f6e7b5a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20201016%2Fs00001%2Fd855986fcf10af9f755d72266645929a.jpg&h=ff07e464\" target=\"_blank\">https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20201016/s00001/d855986fcf10af9f755d72266645929a.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20201016/s00001/d8558c48999771a436a19dc28cf7caad.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20201016%2Fs00001%2Fd8558c48999771a436a19dc28cf7caad.jpg&d=6FpmejEDNbHOA1ae24hao%2FcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=4fd9f4f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20201016%2Fs00001%2Fd8558c48999771a436a19dc28cf7caad.jpg&h=3c7fb770\" target=\"_blank\">https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20201016/s00001/d8558c48999771a436a19dc28cf7caad.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"096e5aafb2fcf5041dd5e61845676b662797fd2e","tid":2246223,"uid":49329,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T01:33:04.000Z","msg":"點解黑警唔死?"},{"pid":"e0f28ae8a9497b630a067b1ac58f00deca1ccf60","tid":2246223,"uid":346701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T01:41:12.000Z","msg":"如果死晒就好"},{"pid":"99621fd603cce65c3623e8b799991590b09cb4ae","tid":2246223,"uid":368147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T01:43:35.000Z","msg":"不如用唒全港啲路啦，返正都係大唒嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b14de478b9e0b0734ec19c696b282d0f83d6771","tid":2246223,"uid":54511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T01:44:56.000Z","msg":"樓上 好人 一世平安 好運 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50bff078df8f3